      "role": "user",
      "content": "i guess. but it doesnt feel temporary. it feels permanent. like i'm just a ghost walking around. if i just... drifted away, or stopped trying to be part of it all, it wouldn't even be traumatic for anyone. it would just be quiet. like i was never even here.",
